1. Definitions

1.1 Licensor
"Licensor" means Fiavo, the sole copyright holder, publisher, and owner of the
Software and all associated intellectual property rights unless otherwise
expressly stated.

1.2 Software
"Software" means NarrativeForge and any other software product, source code,
